text:
‚ÄúIn late 2022, OFAC [‚Ä¶] blacklisted Tornado Cash for its role in laundering virtual currency for malicious cyber actors. The [‚Ä¶] users of Tornado Cash [‚Ä¶] argue that Tornado Cash‚Äôs inclusion on the SDN [Specially Designated National and Blocked Persons] list exceeded OFAC‚Äôs statutory authority. The district court disagreed [‚Ä¶] Contrary to the [Treasury] Department‚Äôs arguments, the immutable smart contracts are not services. So even when we consider OFAC‚Äôs regulatory definitions, the immutable smart contracts are not property because they are not ownable, not contracts, and not services. [‚Ä¶] We hold that OFAC exceeded its statutory authority [‚Ä¶] Accordingly, we reverse and remand to the district court with instructions to grant [the plaintiffs] partial motion for summary judgment.‚Äù

‚Äî US Court of Appeals, Nov. 26, 2024

Massive W for Ethereum, cypherpunk values, & crypto in general. The TC contract address might soon get removed from the OFAC‚Äôs SDN üéâ No more censorship FUD either

show_title: GM Farcaster ep187 Wednesday November 27, 2024 with special guests @eulerlagrange.eth and @dawufi
text:
some news: supercast becomes @super

supercast started as an extension of warpcast

super = better, cast = farcaster client

clean, utilitarian

however, a year in the journey, super is much more than an extension of warpcast

- supercasters and alpha leaks are some of the largest farcaster groupchats
- superanon is the first an the largest anonymous account on farcaster
- supercasters claimed over $1m in airdrops of moxie, degen and most recently, $ANON and $anon
- friends map is the only place where you can see the farcaster location data in a map context
- super artifacts are the new crypto punks ( https://zora.co/@supercast )

every day supercast becomes more independent and very soon, @super will have:
- a free plan, accessible for anyone
- native mobile apps on iOS and android

with proper growth hacks, in 2025 we will be onboarding a similar amount of users to farcaster as warpcast does today

so, makes sense to create and build our own identity
